item.title: The Overseas society presents... I-night: One World
item.author: Michelle Kokkinou,Da Chen,Lydia Lilis,Renos Karamanis,Wasim Khouri,Alexander McFarquhar,
item.description: Next week marks the university’s second International Week of the year (4th – 9th Feburary) with overseas societies coming together to promote cultural diversity and integration at Imperial College. The celebrations build up to Saturday 9th Feburary where the 11th annual International Night will …
